imdb.plot outline: This transformative review series follows the adventures of Jacob Sherwood, Matt Dixon and Toby Mitchell through Creepypasta, a collection of notoriously bad online horror stories. With the help of Gemma, the fans and often Nelson Mandela, they endeavour to showcase every terrible horror story as the poorly written mess it usually is
imdb.title: Bad Creepypasta
plot: 3 British friends read creepypasta, and make fun of the story as it progresses.

This transformative review series follows the adventures of Jacob Sherwood, Matt Dixon and Toby Mitchell through Creepypasta, a collection of notoriously bad online horror stories. With the help of Gemma, the fans and often Nelson Mandela, they endeavour to showcase every terrible horror story as the poorly written mess it usually is::Dom Thorn
